ack|title=14-year-old boy shot at Atlanta middle school, officials say|url=http://usnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/01/31/16793842-14-year-old-boy-shot-at-atlanta-middle-school-officials-say|publisher=NBCNews.com|date=January 31, 2013|accessdate=January 31, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|March 2013}}\n|[[Cape Town]], [[South Africa]]\n|\n|\n|1 injured\n|A grade nine student at Oscar Mpetha High School was stabbed twice in the stomach and sustained cuts to the head.<ref>{{cite news|title=Police probe school stabbing|work=Eyewitness News|date=6 September 2013|url=http://ewn.co.za/2013/09/06/Police-probe-school-stabbing-case|accessdate=7 October 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|April 25, 2013}}\n|[[Mankgodi]], [[Botswana]] \n|Student charged\n|\n|1 injured\n|A student was stabbed and severely wounded at Thobega Junior Secondary School by another student.<ref>{{cite news|title=Back-To-School students in knife stabbing incident|work=Mmegi Online|date=3 April 2013|url=http://www.newsbcc.com/botswana/botswana/back-to-school_students_in_knife_stabbing_incident/420960/|accessdate=7 October 2013|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20131008012724/http://www.newsbcc.com/botswana/botswana/back-to-school_students_in_knife_stabbing_incident/420960/|archivedate=8 October 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|May 7, 2013}}\n|[[Savannah, Georgia]], United States\n|Student charged\n|\n|1 injured\n|A 13-year-old female student was stabbed by another female student at DeRenne Middle School. She was hospitalized for non-life-threatening injuries to the head, shoulder and right arm. The suspect was charged with aggravated assault, possession of a weapon on school property and disrupting public school.<ref>{{cite news|author=Figueredo, Lynda|title=Student charged after stabbing classmate with knife|work=[[WTOC-TV|WTOC]]|date=June 6, 2013|url=http://www.wtoc.com/story/22188987/derenne-middle-school-student-charged-after-stabbing-classmate|accessdate=November 21, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|May 14, 2013}}\n|[[Ca