.org/web/20080203224300/http://www.wbtv.com/home/7083871.html|url-status=dead|title=North Mecklenburg High School Student Dead|archivedate=February 3, 2008}}</ref> Four Charlotte-Mecklenberg schools went on lockdown.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.policeone.com/school-violence/articles/1238487-N-C-high-school-student-shoots-self-after-he-is-confronted-by-police/|title=N.C. high school student shoots self after he is confronted by police|website=policeone.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| May 15, 2007\n| [[Maoming]], [[China]]\n| Wu Jianguo, 17\n| 2 dead\n| 4 injured\n| 17-year-old Wu Jianguo stabbed six classmates with a knife at Dianbai County No. 3 Middle School, killing two of them.<ref>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2007-05/18/content_875126.htm 2 dead in stabbing attack], ''[[China Daily]]'' (May 18, 2007)</ref>\n|-\n| May 23, 2007\n| [[Toronto]], [[Ontario]], Canada\n| ..., 17;<br>..., 17\n| 1 dead\n|\n| 15-year-old Jordan Manners was fatally shot on the campus of [[C.W. Jefferys Collegiate Institute]] in [[Toronto]], [[Ontario]]. Two juveniles were arrested but later acquitted in connection with the shooting, and cannot be identified under the [[Youth Criminal Justice Act]].<ref>[https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2011/05/19/two_acquitted_in_jordan_manners_shooting.html Two acquitted in Jordan Manners shooting], ''[[Toronto Star]]'' (May 19, 2011)</ref>\n|-\n| August 25, 2007\n| [[Jalna district]], India\n| Three students\n| 2 dead\n|\n| Three 12- and 13-year-old students strangled an 8-year-old boy and his 5-year-old brother to death at a boarding school in hope the school would close down, so they would get a day off.<ref>[https://www.usatoday.com/news/world/2007-08-25-india_N.htm Indian police say 3 children killed 2 others], ''[[USA Today]]'' (August 25, 2007)</ref>\n|-\n| September 11, 2007\n| [[Toronto]],<br>[[Ontario]],<br>Canada\n| Unknown\n| 1 dead\n|\n| Dineshkumar Murugiah, a 16-year-old student, was fatally stabbed in an alleyway siding [[Winston Churchill Col