 charged in shooting of teen at West Orange High School|publisher=[[WFTV]]|date=December 5, 2013|accessdate=December 6, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{Dts|December 13, 2013}}\n| [[Centennial, Colorado]], United States\n| Karl Pierson, 18\n| 2 dead\n| \n| 18-year-old male student, Karl Pierson, opened fire with a shotgun at [[Arapahoe High School (Centennial, Colorado)|Arapahoe High School]], critically wounding a 17-year-old female student, Claire Davis. Pierson then committed suicide by shooting himself.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.yahoo.com/gunman-18-wounds-classmate-colorado-school-034437596.html|title=Gunman, 18, wounds classmate in Colorado school|website=yahoo.com}}</ref> Davis died from her injuries eight days later.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://usnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/12/21/22001114-colorado-high-school-shooting-victim-claire-davis-dies?lite|title=Colorado high school shooting victim Claire Davis dies|publisher=[[NBC News]]|author=Becky Bratu|date=December 21, 2013|accessdate=December 21, 2013}}</ref> It was reported that Pierson was looking for the school librarian who had disciplined him, and intended to shoot him, but the faculty member had left the building before the shooting.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/12/13/us/colorado-school-shooting/index.html?hpt=hp_t1|title=Sheriff: Colorado school shooter dead  \u2013 CNN|author1=Ana Cabrera |author2=Chelsea J. Carter |author3=Tom Watkins|website=cnn.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{Dts|December 13, 2013}}\n| [[Vallejo, California]], United States\n| \n|\n|  1 injured\n| A male student's head was slashed with a knife at [[Vallejo High School]] by a 15-year-old female student. The suspect was arrested and charged.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.timesheraldonline.com/news/ci_24716086/vallejo-girl-15-arrested-stabbing-incident|title=Vallejo girl, 15, arrested in stabbing incident|publisher=[[Vallejo Times Herald|Times-Herald]]|date=December 13, 2013|accessdate=December 31, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/w