el]] \n| Student, 15\n| \n| 1 injured\n|A 15-year-old student was stabbed and moderately wounded at a high school. The victim was stabbed twice in the chest with a sharp object during an altercation with another student, and was subsequently hospitalized. A 15-year-old suspect fled the scene and was apprehended.<ref>{{cite news|author=Grave-Lazi, Lidar|title=15-year-old stabbed, moderately wounded at Ashdod school|url=http://www.jpost.com/National-News/15-year-old-stabbed-moderately-wounded-at-Ashdod-school-346920|work=[[Jerusalem Post]]|date=March 30, 2014}}</ref> \n|-\n|{{Dts|April 9, 2014}}\n|[[Murrysville, Pennsylvania]], United States\n| Alex Hribal, 16 (charged)\n|\n| 25 injured\n| In the [[Franklin Regional High School stabbing|Murrysville stabbing]], 16-year-old student Alex Hribal went on a stabbing rampage through classrooms and halls of the Franklin Regional High School. Police said the motive was unknown and identified the student as a sophomore. Seven out of the 22 injured sustained 'life-threatening wounds' to the torso-and-back.<ref>{{cite web|author=McClam, Erin|title=School Stabbing Spree: 20 Hurt in Pittsburgh-Area Bloodbath|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/school-stabbing-spree/school-stabbing-spree-20-hurt-pittsburgh-area-bloodbath-n75536|work=[[NBC News]]|date=April 9, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|April 9, 2014}}\n| [[Greenville, North Carolina]], United States\n|\n|\n| No injuires\n| Just after the lunch hour, at D. H. Conley High School, a car drove past the school. Witnesses said an occupant reached out of a car window and fired shots in the direction of the school. This incident occurred on Worthington and Tull Roads, directly in front of the school. No one was injured.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.witn.com/home/headlines/Lockdown-After-Shots-Fired-Near-Pitt-County-High-School-254581941.html|title=More Security At D.H. Conley High School |date=April 9, 2014|accessdate=April 10, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|April 11, 2014}}\n|[[Detroit]], [[Michigan]], United States\n| Four suspects\n| 1 dead\n| \n| After a Friday evening student awards night, called Grammy Night, 4 men who were affiliated with a gang fired into a crowd in the parking lot of Detroit East English Preparatory Academy. One nineteen-year-old, Darryl Smith, was fatally shot in the head. Smith was not a student at the academy.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.detroitnews.com/article/20140412/METRO01/304120030/Teen-shot-parking-lot-East-English-Village-Preparatory-Academy-Detroit|title=Teen shot in parking lot at East English Village Preparatory Academy in Detroit|date=April 11, 2014|accessdate=April 12, 2014|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413150345/http://www.detroitnews.com/article/20140412/METRO01/304120030/Teen-shot-parking-lot-East-English-Village-Preparatory-Academy-Detroit|archivedate=April 13, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.clickondetroit.com/news/craig-4-gang-members-shot-into-crowd-killed-teenager/25449014|title=Detroit teen shot after school event dies|date=April 13, 2014|accessdate=April 14, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140414005320/http://www.clickondetroit.com/news/craig-4-gang-members-shot-into-crowd-killed-teenager/25449014|archive-date=April 14, 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|April 12, 2014}}\n|[[Pietermaritzburg, South Africa]]\n| Multiple suspects\n| \n| 4 injured\n|Four students were stabbed and injured during a fight on a school bus. One of the students suffered severe facial injuries. The incident is believed to be gang-related.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/Pupils-stabbed-on-school-bus-in-KZN-20140412|title=Pupils stabbed on school bus in KZN|publisher=[[News24]]|date=April 12, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|April 15, 2014}}\n|[[Brampton, Ontario]], Canada \n| Three suspects\n| \n| 1 injured\n|A 17-year-old male student was stabbed in the hallway of [[St. Roch Catholic Secondary School]], and was hospitalized for non-life-threatening 