ted to open fire in the school cafeteria at 11:33&nbsp;a.m. Multiple shots were fired in the process, and one student was struck in the chest. The victims was driven to a nearby hospital suffering non-life-threatening wounds. The suspect was taken into custody without further incident.<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.mattoon.k12.il.us/vnews/display.v/ART/59c2b2193096f |title = Mattoon Community Unit School District 2 \u2013 MHS students, staff secure following shooting |website= www.mattoon.k12.il.us |language = en |access-date = September 21, 2017 |url-status = live |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170921144403/https://www.mattoon.k12.il.us/vnews/display.v/ART/59c2b2193096f |archivedate = September 21, 2017 |df = mdy-all }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://time.com/4950377/mattoon-illinois-high-school-shooting/ |title = Suspect in Custody After Injuring One in Shooting at Illinois High School |last = Press |first = Associated |website= Time |access-date = September 21, 2017 |url-status = dead |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170920231817/http://time.com/4950377/mattoon-illinois-high-school-shooting/ |archivedate = September 20, 2017 |df = mdy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|September 26, 2017}}\n|[[Bronx, New York]], US \n| Student \n| 1 dead\n| 1 injured\n| Abel Cedeno killing incident. A 15-year-old student was stabbed to death and a 16-year-old was critically injured at Urban Assembly School for Wildlife Conservation, a grades 6-12 school. An 18-year-old student was charged with murder. It was speculated that the suspect was bothered by the victims' homophobic comments.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/09/27/nyregion/high-school-stabbing-bronx.html|title=High school stabbing in the Bronx|newspaper=[[New York Times]]|date=September 27, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|October 14, 2017}}\n|Lokichogio, Kenya\n| Group of gunmen, lead by student\n| 7 dead\n| 20 injured\n| A suspended student led a group of gunmen on a shooting spree at Lokichogio Mixed Secondary School.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://apnews.com/6ddf8c73ac39432abbfe9aa7f408850f/7-killed-in-Kenya-high-school-shooting-during-raid|title=7 dead in Kenya school shooting in suspected revenge attack|date=October 14, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|October 20, 2017}}\n|[[Goi\u00e2nia]], [[Goi\u00e1s]], [[Brazil]]\n| \n| 2 dead\n| 4 injured\n| [[Goyases School Shooting]]. A 14-year-old eighth-grade student opened fire with a .40-caliber handgun at Goyases College, killing two students and wounding four others. He was arrested. \n|-\n|{{Dts|November 15, 2017}}\n|[[Yuanjiang]], [[Hunan province]], China\n| Student, 16\n| 1 dead\n| \n| A 47-year-old teacher was stabbed to death by a 16-year-old student at No. 3 High School.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rfa.org/english/news/china/hunan-stabbing-11152017142202.html|title=Chinese Police Hold Teen After Fatal Stabbing in Hunan High School|publisher=RFA.org}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|December 7, 2017}}\n|[[Aztec, New Mexico]], US \n| William Atchison, 21\n| 3 dead\n| \n| [[Aztec High School shooting]]. A 21-year-old former [[Aztec High School]] student, William Atchison, disguised himself as a student and shot two students to death, and then committed suicide. He was believed by police to have no connections with the victims. \n|-\n|{{Dts|December 12, 2017}}\n|[[Changqing, Loudi|Changqing]], [[Hunan province]], China\n| Student, 21\n| 1 dead\n| \n| A 13-year-old student was fatally stabbed with a sword at Quan Feng Secondary School by a classmate. It was reported that the suspect was playing with the classmate before he was apparently accidentally stabbed.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theepochtimes.com/13-year-old-boy-impaled-by-sword-as-he-played-with-classmate_2387201.html|title=13-Year-Old Boy Impaled by Sword as He \u2018Played\u2019 With Classmate|newspaper=Epoch Times}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|January 19, 2018}}\n|[[Ulan-Ude]], Russia\n| Student, 15\n|\n| 6 injured\n| Five seventh-graders and their teacher were wounded when a ninth-grader in Buryatia's capital Ulan-Ude, near Lake Baikal in Siberia, attacked them with an axe and burned the classroom with a Molotov cocktail. One student was in critical condition. The attacker was detained and hospitalised after he tried to commit suicide.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/01/19/teen-russia-axes-students-burns-classroom-third-school-attack/ |title=Teen in Russia axes students and burns classroom in third school attack  in a week |publisher=telegraph.co.uk}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|January 22, 2018}}\n|[[Italy, Texas]] \n| \n|\n| 1 injured\n|A 16-year-old male student fired at a 15-year-old classmate in the cafeteria of [[Italy High School]]. The gunman left the school immediately after opening fire.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2018/01/22/shooting-at-texas-high-school-suspect-in-custody-police-say.html|title=Texas high school shooting leaves 1 student wounded; suspect in custody, police say|first=Katherine|last=Lam|date=22 January 2018|website=foxnews.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/texas-teen-charged-assault-italy-high-school-shooting-n840301|title=16-year-old boy charged in Texas shooting, wounded student remains hospitalized|website=nbcnews.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kwtx.com/content/news/Gunman-in-custody-Monday-at-Italy-High-School-some-injured-470519863.html|title=Paramedic: Girl wounded in area school shooting bravest \u2018I\u2019ve ever seen\u2019|first=John|last=Carroll|website=kwtx.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|January 22, 2018}}\n|[[New Orleans, Louisiana]] \n| \n|\n| 1 injured\n|Shots were fired from a truck in the parking lot of NET Charter High School, targeting a crowd of students during lunch time. One student was slightly injured, apparently from injuries unrelated to gunfire. One person was arrested in connection with the shooting.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.npr.org/2018/01/24/580433745/a-look-at-all-11-school-shootings-that-took-place-in-the-first-23-days-of-2018|title=A Look at all 11 school shooting that took place in the first 23 days of 2018|work=[[MPRNews]]|access-date=January 25, 2018|language=en-US}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|January 23, 2018}}\n|[[Benton, Kentucky]], US\n| Gabe Parker, 15 (charged) \n| 2 dead\n| 18 injured\n|[[Marshall County High School shooting]]: A 15-year-old male student shot 16 people in the lobby at Marshall County High School and caused non-gunshot injuries to 4 others. Two 15-year-old students died: one killed at the scene, another died of wounds at [[Vanderbilt University Medical Center|Vanderbilt Medical Center]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/kentucky-shooting-marshall-county-high-school-students-shot-today-2018-01-23-live-updates/|title=Kentucky school shooting: 2 dead, 15 more shot at Marshall County High School -- live updates|website=cbsnews.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/one-dead-after-shooting-kentucky-high-school-multiple-victims-reported-n840171|title=Two dead, suspect in custody after shooting at Kentucky high school|website=nbcnews.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/2018/01/23/us/kentucky-high-school-shooting/index.html|title=Kentucky school shooting: 2 students killed, 18 injured|author1=Holly Yan |author2=AnneClaire Stapleton |author3=Paul P. Murphy|website=cnn.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|February 14, 2018}}\n|[[Parkland, Florida]], US\n| Nikolas Cruz, 19\n| 17 dead\n| 17 injured\n|[[Stoneman Douglas High School shooting]]\n|-\n|-\n|{{Dts|March 20,2018}}\n|[[Great Mills, Maryland]], US\n| Austin Rollins, 17\n| 2 dead\n| 1 injured\n| A 17-year-old male student, armed with a handgun, shot and fatally injured a female student (with whom he had a prior relationship), then began firing at random people in the school, wounding a male student. The suspect shot himself in the head fatally after engaging with the school's SRO, while the school resource officer simultaneously shot at him.<ref